 photoelectric performance.\nFinally, we emphasize the importance and universality of spatial inversion\nsymmetry broken in layered materials beyond the 3R bilayer BX to realize the\nco-regulation of ferroelectric and photovoltaics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Apr 2021 11:56:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-08"}
