y be seen as intermittent\nstructures. Statistical features of Lagrangian paths and entropy values are\nthus fixed by the fluctuation theorems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Apr 2021 14:07:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 4 Jun 2021 09:54:23 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 24 Jun 2022 15:26:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-27"}
