 non-contact poses. The code and data are available for research\npurposes at https://tuch.is.tue.mpg.de.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Apr 2021 15:10:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 8 Apr 2021 07:29:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-09"}
